            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "We have a lot of memories here. Students also gain so much knowledge..But every students tries to get marks their curriculum is absolutely best curriculum. Most of the students have there own memories.I am also a student of this school this is the honest review from me that every teacher tries to make the student to educate.There is also a canteen in the school you can purchase any snacks in break and lunch time. Specially for 10th class students they are taking very special care. They also have a star programme for 10th class students in this programme every student learn all the 10th syllabus.There two sessions in day and they give some time for study and they keep exams so students can also learn the syllabus very fastly.There the so many batches here you can join as per your wish if you want to gain IIT you should join in cbatch of ipl. if you want to gain NEET you should join in mbatch. For civils you can join in snatch. There is a good faculty the teachers are very friendly and always help the students to gain good marks. The tecahers also tell us how to gain good marks in public exams and method of writing. They have a special font in writing it is Lucida hand writing which looks very attractive and impressive. This hand writing is very easy to leran and it is very impressive. In public exams the examiner correct the paper and give full marks because of your hand writing.The playground is also very nice the pet sir tells you the different games. Which is very helpful to your health.All most all the students can gain better knowledge. So finally the school is very good and best school to gain knowledge.",
